<subSubSection lastPageId="2" lastPageNumber="208" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="0.[136,1452,1777,2089]" lastBlockId="1.[136,1452,159,327]" lastPageId="1" lastPageNumber="207" pageId="0" pageNumber="206">
<emphasis box="[136,372,1777,1801]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="206">Note on the typification</emphasis>
: 
<collectingCounty box="[385,406,1777,1800]" pageId="0" pageNumber="206">In</collectingCounty>
the herbarium BOLO there is a specimen [without number] collected by 
<collectorName box="[1151,1239,1777,1801]" pageId="0" pageNumber="206">Gussone</collectorName>
that was received by 
<collectingMunicipality box="[136,232,1813,1837]" pageId="0" pageNumber="206">Bertoloni</collectingMunicipality>
in 1822. 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F70A34FFCBF57C96A09412FEBF372E:8E81EDF9FFCBF57E976C9538FE9E3729" box="[324,339,1813,1836]" country="Italy" county="In" municipality="Bertoloni" name="It" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" stateProvince="Sicilia">It</location>
perfectly agrees with the description in 
<bibRefCitation author="Bertoloni, A." box="[739,911,1813,1837]" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" pagination="343 - 344" refId="ref1434" refString="Bertoloni, A. (1838) Anethum. In: Flora Italica: sistens plantas in Italia et in insulis circumstantibus sponte nascentes. Vol. 3 (3). Richardi Masii, Bononiae [Bologna], pp. 343 - 344." type="book chapter" year="1838">Bertoloni (1838)</bibRefCitation>
. 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F70A34FFCBF57C96A09412FEBF372E:8E81EDF9FFCBF57E95BF9538FC093728" box="[919,964,1813,1837]" country="Italy" county="In" municipality="Bertoloni" name="This" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" stateProvince="Sicilia">This</location>
specimen is not suitable for typification because it indicates the distribution in 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F70A34FFCBF57C96A09412FEBF372E:8E81EDF9FFCBF57E97939514FE3A3754" box="[443,503,1849,1873]" country="Italy" county="In" municipality="Bertoloni" name="South" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" stateProvince="Sicilia">South</location>
<collectingCountry box="[510,556,1849,1873]" name="Italy" pageId="0" pageNumber="206">Italy</collectingCountry>
(“nei campi coltivati di 
<collectingRegion box="[807,874,1849,1873]" country="Italy" name="Sicilia" pageId="0" pageNumber="206">Sicilia</collectingRegion>
, e di 
<collectingRegion box="[930,1019,1849,1873]" country="Italy" name="Calabria" pageId="0" pageNumber="206">Calabria</collectingRegion>
” – whereas the protologue refers to 
<collectingRegion box="[1392,1452,1849,1873]" country="Italy" name="Sicilia" pageId="0" pageNumber="206">Sicily</collectingRegion>
only) and not a gathering locality. 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F70A34FFCBF57C96A09412FEBF372E:8E81EDF9FFCBF57E97C19570FD953770" box="[489,600,1885,1909]" country="Italy" county="In" municipality="Bertoloni" name="Specimens" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" stateProvince="Sicilia">Specimens</location>
collected by 
<collectorName box="[738,826,1885,1909]" pageId="0" pageNumber="206">Gussone</collectorName>
are not present at FI and PAL. 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F70A34FFCBF57C96A09412FEBF372E:8E81EDF9FFCBF57E92569570FB3E3770" box="[1150,1267,1885,1909]" country="Italy" county="In" municipality="Bertoloni" name="In Gussone" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" stateProvince="Sicilia">In Gussone</location>
<collectingRegion box="[1274,1338,1885,1909]" country="Italy" name="Sicilia" pageId="0" pageNumber="206">Sicilia</collectingRegion>
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F70A34FFCBF57C96A09412FEBF372E:8E81EDF9FFCBF57E93699570FA663770" box="[1345,1451,1885,1909]" country="Italy" county="In" municipality="Bertoloni" name="Collection" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" stateProvince="Sicilia">Collection</location>
at NAP, 
<specimenCount box="[221,401,1921,1945]" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" type="generic">twelve specimens</specimenCount>
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Moris" authorityYear="1841" baseAuthorityName="Gussone" baseAuthorityYear="1827" box="[434,606,1921,1945]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Apiaceae" genus="Ridolfia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Apiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="segetum">
<emphasis box="[434,606,1921,1945]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="206">Ridolfia segetum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from several localities are preserved. 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F70A34FFCBF57C96A09412FEBF372E:8E81EDF9FFCBF57E95F495ACFC34379C" box="[988,1017,1921,1945]" country="Italy" county="In" municipality="Bertoloni" name="As" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" stateProvince="Sicilia">As</location>
usual in 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F70A34FFCBF57C96A09412FEBF372E:8E81EDF9FFCBF57E927C95ACFAD1379C" box="[1108,1308,1921,1945]" country="Italy" county="In" municipality="Bertoloni" name="Gussone Collection" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" stateProvince="Sicilia">Gussone Collection</location>
(see 
<bibRefCitation author="Pasquale, G. A." pageId="0" pageNumber="206" refId="ref2037" refString="Pasquale, G. A. (1871) Documenti biografici di Giovanni Gussone. Atti Accademia Pontaniana: I- 55." type="book" year="1871">Pasquale 1871</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="La Valva, V." box="[200,357,1957,1981]" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" pagination="515 - 537" refId="ref1913" refString="La Valva, V. (1993) La Collezione Gussone Sicilia. Webbia 48: 515 - 537." type="journal article" year="1993">La Valva, 1993</bibRefCitation>
), only the first sheet of the series has detailed label with all the nomenclatural, ecological, and distributional data. 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F70A34FFCBF57C96A09412FEBF372E:8E81EDF9FFCBF57E96E895E4FED537E4" box="[192,280,1993,2017]" country="Italy" county="In" municipality="Bertoloni" name="Separate" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" stateProvince="Sicilia">Separate</location>
labels with “field” data are put together in the first sheet or in the next ones. 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F70A34FFCBF57C96A09412FEBF372E:8E81EDF9FFCBF57E921995E4FB5937E4" box="[1073,1172,1993,2017]" country="Italy" county="In" municipality="Bertoloni" name="Duplicate" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" stateProvince="Sicilia">Duplicate</location>
specimens originally don’t bear label. 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F70A34FFCBF57C96A09412FEBF372E:8E81EDF9FFCBF57E96DF95C0FEC13801" box="[247,268,2029,2052]" country="Italy" county="In" municipality="Bertoloni" name="In" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" stateProvince="Sicilia">In</location>
this case, only later 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F70A34FFCBF57C96A09412FEBF372E:8E81EDF9FFCBF57E97F395C0FD3B3800" box="[475,758,2029,2053]" country="Italy" county="In" municipality="Bertoloni" name="Giuseppe Antonio Pasquale" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" stateProvince="Sicilia">Giuseppe Antonio Pasquale</location>
, student and disciple of 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F70A34FFCBF57C96A09412FEBF372E:8E81EDF9FFCBF57E95C295C0FB893800" box="[1002,1092,2029,2053]" country="Italy" county="In" municipality="Bertoloni" name="Gussone" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" stateProvince="Sicilia">Gussone</location>
, added the labels with indication of date, place of gathering, and collector in the duplicates of 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F70A34FFCBF57C96A09412FEBF372E:8E81EDF9FFCBF57E94FF9A3CFC67382C" box="[727,938,2065,2089]" country="Italy" county="In" municipality="Bertoloni" name="Gussone Collections" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" stateProvince="Sicilia">Gussone Collections</location>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Pasquale, G. A." box="[951,1102,2065,2089]" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" refId="ref2037" refString="Pasquale, G. A. (1871) Documenti biografici di Giovanni Gussone. Atti Accademia Pontaniana: I- 55." type="book" year="1871">Pasquale 1871</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="La Valva, V." box="[1113,1270,2065,2089]" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" pagination="515 - 537" refId="ref1913" refString="La Valva, V. (1993) La Collezione Gussone Sicilia. Webbia 48: 515 - 537." type="journal article" year="1993">La Valva, 1993</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Santangelo, A. &amp; Idolo, M. &amp; La Valva, V." lastPageId="1" lastPageNumber="207" pageId="0" pageNumber="206" pagination="368 - 369" refId="ref2160" refString="Santangelo, A., Idolo, M. &amp; La Valva, V. (2005) La collezione Gussone Generale (NAP). Informatore Botanico Italiano 37 (1, parte a): 368 - 369." type="journal article" year="2005">
Santangelo 
<emphasis box="[1400,1445,2065,2089]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="206">et al</emphasis>
. 2005
</bibRefCitation>
). 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F70A34FFCBF57C96A09412FEBF372E:8E81EDF9FFCAF57F96F8928DFEFB30B2" box="[208,310,160,183]" country="Italy" county="In" municipality="Bertoloni" name="Moreover" pageId="1" pageNumber="207" stateProvince="Sicilia">Moreover</location>
, 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F70A34FFCBF57C96A09412FEBF372E:8E81EDF9FFCAF57F976892B2FE5530B2" box="[320,408,159,183]" country="Italy" county="In" municipality="Bertoloni" name="Gussone" pageId="1" pageNumber="207" stateProvince="Sicilia">Gussone</location>
began to add on the label the date of collection only after 1824. 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F70A34FFCBF57C96A09412FEBF372E:8E81EDF9FFCAF57F9200928DFBF030B2" box="[1064,1085,160,183]" country="Italy" county="In" municipality="Bertoloni" name="In" pageId="1" pageNumber="207" stateProvince="Sicilia">In</location>
this sense, almost all the specimens of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Moris" authorityYear="1841" baseAuthorityName="Gussone" baseAuthorityYear="1827" box="[163,275,196,219]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Apiaceae" genus="Ridolfia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Apiales" pageId="1" pageNumber="207" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="segetum">
<emphasis box="[163,275,196,219]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="207">R. segetum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F70A34FFCBF57C96A09412FEBF372E:8E81EDF9FFCAF57F971A92EEFE4730DE" box="[306,394,195,219]" country="Italy" county="In" municipality="Bertoloni" name="Gussone" pageId="1" pageNumber="207" stateProvince="Sicilia">Gussone</location>
<collectingRegion box="[400,464,195,219]" country="Italy" name="Sicilia" pageId="1" pageNumber="207">Sicilia</collectingRegion>
collection can be considered original material; in fact, only 
<specimenCount box="[1072,1211,195,219]" pageId="1" pageNumber="207" type="generic">one specimen</specimenCount>
bears the label with the indication of the date of gathering (
<date box="[500,666,231,255]" pageId="1" pageNumber="207" value="1841-06-28">
<collectingDate box="[500,666,231,255]" pageId="1" pageNumber="207" value="1841-06-28">28 giugno 1841</collectingDate>
</date>
), all the other ones reporting only the gathering localities, showing that they have been collected by 
<collectorName box="[371,459,267,291]" pageId="1" pageNumber="207">Gussone</collectorName>
before 1824. We selected the first sheet of the series as lectotype. Note that we consider the second sheet (
<figureCitation box="[202,263,303,327]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="3.[136,229,2022,2044]" captionTargetBox="[191,1396,190,1998]" captionTargetId="figure-28@3.[191,1396,190,1998]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURE 3. Isolectotype of Meum segetum Guss. (NAP, Gussone Sicilia Collection [without number])." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6821005" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6821005/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="207">Fig. 3</figureCitation>
), with its label written by Pasquale (as above), as a duplicate of the first one, and so an isolectotype.
</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6821001" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6821001" box="[136,1015,2046,2068]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6821001/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="207" startId="1.[136,229,2046,2068]" targetBox="[226,1362,350,2019]" targetPageId="1">
