<emphasis bold="true" box="[136,254,2046,2068]" pageId="1" pageNumber="207">FIGURE 1.</emphasis>
Lectotype of 
<taxonomicName authority="All." authorityName="All." box="[387,604,2046,2068]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Apiaceae" genus="Anethum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Apiales" pageId="1" pageNumber="207" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pusillum">
<emphasis box="[387,562,2046,2067]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="207">Anethum pusillum</emphasis>
All.
</taxonomicName>
(TO, Allioni Collection [without number].
</paragraph>
